<p>Hello, <%= @user.name %></p>

<p>Dead Moroz has chosen you to accomplish mission of bringing happiness to all children of the world
You have no right to reject this invitation.</p>

<% if @resource.invitation_due_at %>
  <p><%= t("devise.mailer.invitation_instructions.accept_until", due_date: l(@resource.invitation_due_at, format: :'devise.mailer.invitation_instructions.accept_until_format')) %></p>
<% end %>

<p>If you don't accept invitation before tine is over, it would be your mistake.
To accept it go to the link below</p>

<% if Rails.env.production? %>
  <%= link_to 'Accept Invitation', "#{Rails.application.credentials.client_domain_prod}/accept_elf_invitation?invitation_token=#{@token}" %>
<% else %>
  <%= link_to 'Accept Invitation', "#{Rails.application.credentials.client_domain_dev}/accept_elf_invitation?invitation_token=#{@token}" %>
<% end %>